    .container-fluid.project-details-container
        .row.project-details-row.text-end.mx-5.justify-content-center
            .col-12.project-details-headline-col.p-0.text-center
                h2.project-details-headline Atlantis Euphoria
            .col-10.project-details-headline-col.p-0.text-start
                div.project-details-text We are pleased to present to you the new project of the Atlantis Bulgaria Holdings group: <strong>Atlantis Euphoria</strong>. The project is located in the heart of the new Horizont Quarter and guarantees an harmonious combination of urban comfort and peaceful living.
                div.project-details-text The project will be located in the Horizon district, in a communicative but at the same time peaceful environment, which provides quick and convenient access to everything you need in your daily life.     
                div.project-details-text The Euphoria project will include a total of 292 apartments, including two-room, three-room and four-room apartments with an area of ​​between 72 square meters and 269 square meters. They will be divided between 6 separate buildings, each with 9 floors. The residential complex will be closed, and will offer many services for the residents.     
                div.project-details-text The complex will have a green park, where there will be designated places for relaxation and leisure such as picnic areas, yoga and fitness areas, game tables, a children's playground and covered parking.
                div.project-details-text The purpose of the project is to create positive feelings among the residents of the new complex built on two levels - inside and outside the complex. In choosing the name "Euphoria", the developers of the project chose a word synonymous with joy, optimism, enthusiasm and momentum.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Location
                div.project-details-text A few minutes' walk from the complex, there are shopping centers such as Burgess Plaza Mall, Kaufland, Metro, Lidl, and also a central bus station - Arena Burgess.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Horizont Quarter
                div.project-details-text The Atlantis Euphoria project is going to be built in the heart of the Horizont Quarter - the newest residential neighborhood in Burgas and in the coming years the area is going to be developed in a way that has never been seen before in the city.
                div.project-details-text As part of the planning of the district as a combination of modern residential buildings and also a nature preserve, a wide and green park of about 50,000 square meters will be built.
                div.project-details-text The district is planned to be populated mainly by young families, so it will be possible to find kindergartens, parks with playgrounds, as well as designated areas for picnics and BBQ's.
                div.project-detail-img-container.d-flex.justify-content-center   
                    img.project-details-img(src='https://dirabulgaritbucket.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/atlantis-aria-3-images/1718892982826-atlantis-aria-3-horizont.webp' alt='Geographical representation of the Horizont quarter in Burgas Bulgaria')
                div.project-details-text.text-center <i>Horizont Quarter</i>
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Architecture
                div.project-details-text The structure of the buildings will differ in the functional layouts and the tall glass showcases, a construction concept that aims to ensure maximum access to natural sunlight and visual natural views in each apartment.
                div.project-details-text The most important point in the design and realization of the residential complex is the creation of conditions for harmony and peace, both inside and outside the house. Above all, it focuses on quality construction and environmental friendliness.
                h3.project-details-sub-headline Atlantis Bulgaria Holdings
                div.project-details-text Atlantis Construction Group is a real estate entrepreneurship company with rich experience in developing projects throughout Burgas and Sofia for more than 25 years. 
                div.project-details-text The group consists of several companies working in different fields. What unites the group is the mission to create a comfortable environment and a peaceful life in the big city, through the application of modern concepts in construction.
                div.project-details-text Atlantis Bulgaria specializes in real estate development in areas with high investment attractiveness by building profitable projects with long-term thinking. The result is dozens of residential buildings that have been successfully completed and have yielded maximum returns for property owners.    
                div.project-details-text Thanks to strategic planning, all the houses built by the Atlantis Bulgaria Group have become a harmonious combination of natural beauty and a creative expression of modern architecture. It is important to note that thanks to their activities in Burgas and Sofia, over time, the cultural awareness has increased that nature is an integral part of life in the city and that it has a great impact on the health, safety and well-being of each and every one.

